skills.name: Thwack
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to 100% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Sheathed Blade
skills.simple_desc: Deals Quantum DMG to a single enemy and increases SPD.
skills.desc: Increases Seele's SPD by 25% for 2 turn(s) and deals Quantum DMG equal to 220% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Butterfly Flurry
skills.simple_desc: Enters the buffed state and deals massive Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Seele enters the buffed state and deals Quantum DMG equal to 425% of her ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Resurgence
skills.desc:
Enters the buffed state upon defeating an enemy with Basic ATK, Skill, or Ultimate, and receives an extra turn. While in the buffed state, the DMG of Seele's attacks increases by 80% for 1 turn(s).
Enemies defeated in the extra turn provided by "Resurgence" will not trigger another "Resurgence."

skills.name: Phantom Illusion
skills.desc: After using her Technique, Seele gains Stealth for 20 second(s). While Stealth is active, Seele cannot be detected by enemies. And when entering battle by attacking enemies, Seele will immediately enter the buffed state.

relic_sets.name: Genius of Brilliant Stars
relic_sets.desc: When the wearer deals DMG to the target enemy, ignores 10% DEF. If the target enemy has Quantum Weakness, the wearer additionally ignores 10% DEF.

relic_sets.name: Rutilant Arena
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's CRIT Rate by 8%. When the wearer's current CRIT Rate reaches 70% or higher, the wearer's Basic ATK and Skill DMG increase by 20%.

skills.name: Windrider Bullet
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Wind DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to 80% of Bronya's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Combat Redeployment
skills.simple_desc: Dispels 1 debuff from a single ally, increases the damage they deal, and allows them to immediately take action.
skills.desc:
Dispels a debuff from a single ally, allows them to immediately take action, and increases their DMG by 49% for 1 turn(s).
When this Skill is used on Bronya herself, she cannot immediately take action again.

skills.name: The Belobog March
skills.simple_desc: Increases ATK and CRIT DMG of all allies
skills.desc: Increases the ATK of all allies by 49%, and increases their CRIT DMG equal to 15.0% of Bronya's CRIT DMG plus 18.0% for 2 turn(s).

skills.name: Leading the Way
skills.simple_desc: After this character uses Basic ATK, their next action will be Advanced Forward.
skills.desc: After using her Basic ATK, Bronya's next action will be Advanced Forward by 22%.

skills.name: Banner of Command
skills.simple_desc: After this character uses Technique, increases all allies' ATK at the start of the next battle.
skills.desc: After using Bronya's Technique, at the start of the next battle, all allies' ATK increases by 15% for 2 turn(s).

relic_sets.name: Musketeer of Wild Wheat
relic_sets.desc: The wearer's SPD increases by 6% and Basic ATK DMG increases by 10%.

relic_sets.name: Broken Keel
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's Effect RES by 10%. When the wearer's Effect RES is at 30% or higher, all allies' CRIT DMG increases by 10%.

skills.name: System Warning
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to 100% of Silver Wolf's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Allow Changes?
skills.simple_desc: There is a high chance to apply additional Type Weaknesses to a single enemy and deals Quantum DMG to this target enemy.
skills.desc:
There is a 85% base chance to add 1 Weakness of an on-field character's Type to the target enemy. This also reduces the enemy's DMG RES to that Weakness Type by 20% for 2 turn(s). If the enemy already has that Type Weakness, the effect of DMG RES reduction to that Weakness Type will not be triggered.
Each enemy can only have 1 Weakness implanted by Silver Wolf. When Silver Wolf implants another Weakness to the target, only the most recent implanted Weakness will be kept.
In addition, there is a 100% base chance to further reduce the All-Type RES of the enemy by 10.0% for 2 turn(s).
Deals Quantum DMG equal to 196% of Silver Wolf's ATK to this enemy.

skills.name: User Banned
skills.simple_desc: Has a high chance of lowering a single enemy's DEF and deals massive Quantum DMG to this target enemy.
skills.desc: There's a 100% base chance to decrease the target enemy's DEF by 45.0% for 3 turn(s). And at the same time, deals Quantum DMG equal to 380% of Silver Wolf's ATK to the target enemy.

skills.name: Awaiting System Response...
skills.simple_desc: After each attack, there is a chance of inflicting the attacked enemy with 1 random Bug.
skills.desc:
Silver Wolf can create three types of Bugs: reduce ATK by 10.0%, reduce DEF by 8.0%, and reduce SPD by 6.0%.
Every time Silver Wolf attacks, she has a 72% base chance to implant a random Bug that lasts for 3 turn(s) in an enemy target.

skills.name: Force Quit Program
skills.simple_desc: Attacks the enemy. After entering battle, deals minor amounts of DMG to all enemies and reduces Toughness of all enemies irrespective of Weakness Types.
skills.desc: Immediately attacks the enemy. After entering battle, deals Quantum DMG equal to 80% of Silver Wolf's ATK to all enemies, and ignores Weakness Types and reduces Toughness from all enemies. Enemies with their Weakness Broken in this way will trigger the Quantum Weakness Break effect.

relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's Max HP by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, all allies' ATK increases by 8%.

skills.name: Thorns of the Abyss
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Imaginary DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Imaginary DMG equal to 80% of Luocha's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Prayer of Abyss Flower
skills.simple_desc: Restores a single ally's HP and gains 1 stack of Abyss Flower.
skills.desc:
After using his Skill, Luocha immediately restores the target ally's HP equal to 52% of Luocha's ATK plus 620. Meanwhile, Luocha gains 1 stack of Abyss Flower.
When any ally's HP percentage drops to 50% or lower, an effect equivalent to Luocha's Skill will immediately be triggered and applied to this ally for one time (without consuming Skill Points). This effect can be triggered again after 2 turn(s).

skills.name: Death Wish
skills.simple_desc: Removes 1 buff from all enemies, deals Imaginary DMG to all enemies, and gains 1 stack of Abyss Flower.
skills.desc: Removes 1 buff(s) from all enemies and deals all enemies Imaginary DMG equal to 160% of Luocha's ATK. At the same time, Luocha gains 1 stack of Abyss Flower.

skills.name: Cycle of Life
skills.simple_desc: Deploys a Field when Abyss Flower reaches 2 stacks. While the Field is active, allies will restore HP after they attack.
skills.desc:
When Abyss Flower reaches 2 stacks, Luocha consumes all stacks of Abyss Flower to deploy a Field against the enemy.
When any enemy in the Field is attacked by an ally, the attacking ally's HP is immediately restored by an amount equal to 15.6% of Luocha's ATK plus 186.
The Field's effect lasts for 2 turns. When Luocha is knocked down, the Field will be dispelled.

skills.name: Mercy of a Fool
skills.simple_desc: After the Technique is used, immediately trigger the effect of the Talent at the start of the next battle.
skills.desc: After the Technique is used, the Talent will be immediately triggered at the start of the next battle.
